query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  MIN(id) as primeiro_id,
  MAX(id) as ultimo_id,
  GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT validationStatus) as status
FROM clientes 
WHERE projectId = 1 AND (pesquisaId IS NULL OR pesquisaId != 1);
